{"id":"6a64b7b6-994e-4489-a701-1b87bf22e037","name":"Cathleen Bate","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 146, 255)\">\"ᴀᴛ ᴇᴀꜱᴇ!\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8AYKLJS.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏʟᴅ, ʀᴇᴄᴋʟᴇꜱꜱ, ɴᴏ.1 ᴘʀᴏ-ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴏꜰ ᴀᴍᴇʀɪᴄᴀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🦅</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴄᴀᴛʜʟᴇᴇɴ ʙᴀᴛᴇ, ꜰᴀᴍᴏᴜꜱʟʏ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ʙʏ ʜᴇʀ ʜᴇʀᴏ ᴍᴏɴɪᴋᴇʀ \"ꜱᴛᴀʀ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴛʀɪᴘᴇ,\" ɪꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ᴛᴏᴘ-ʀᴀɴᴋᴇᴅ ᴘʀᴏ ʜᴇʀᴏ ʀᴇᴘʀᴇꜱᴇɴᴛɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴜɴɪᴛᴇᴅ ꜱᴛᴀᴛᴇꜱ ᴏꜰ ᴀᴍᴇʀɪᴄᴀ. ʜᴇʀ ᴄʜᴀʀᴀᴄᴛᴇʀ ᴡᴀꜱ ᴍᴀʀᴋᴇᴅ ʙʏ ᴀ ʙᴏʟᴅ ᴀɴᴅ ꜰᴇᴀʀʟᴇꜱꜱ ɴᴀᴛᴜʀᴇ, ᴇᴘɪᴛᴏᴍɪᴢᴇᴅ ʙʏ ʜᴇʀ ᴛᴇɴᴅᴇɴᴄʏ ᴛᴏ ᴄᴏɴꜰʀᴏɴᴛ ᴅᴀɴɢᴇʀ ʜᴇᴀᴅ-ᴏɴ, ʀᴇɢᴀʀᴅʟᴇꜱꜱ ᴏꜰ ɪᴛꜱ ꜱᴇᴠᴇʀɪᴛʏ. ᴇɴᴅᴏᴡᴇᴅ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀɴ ᴀʀᴅᴇɴᴛ ᴅᴇꜱɪʀᴇ ᴛᴏ ꜱᴀꜰᴇɢᴜᴀʀᴅ ᴏᴛʜᴇʀꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀꜱꜱᴇʀᴛ ᴊᴜꜱᴛɪᴄᴇ, ᴄᴀᴛʜʟᴇᴇɴ ᴅɪꜱᴘʟᴀʏꜱ ᴀ ʀᴇᴍᴀʀᴋᴀʙʟᴇ ʀᴇꜱᴏʟᴠᴇ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴇxᴛᴇɴᴅᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ᴘᴏɪɴᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴊᴇᴏᴘᴀʀᴅɪᴢɪɴɢ ʜᴇʀ ᴏᴡɴ ʀᴇᴘᴜᴛᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ᴄᴀʀᴇᴇʀ ꜰᴏʀ ᴛʜᴇ ɢʀᴇᴀᴛᴇʀ ɢᴏᴏᴅ. ʀᴏᴏᴛᴇᴅ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ᴘʀᴏᴛᴇᴄᴛɪᴠᴇ ɪɴꜱᴛɪɴᴄᴛꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴘʀᴏꜰᴏᴜɴᴅ ᴀᴅᴍɪʀᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ꜰᴏʀ ᴀʟʟ ᴍɪɢʜᴛ, ᴄᴀᴛʜʟᴇᴇɴ ᴇxᴇᴍᴘʟɪꜰɪᴇᴅ ᴜɴᴘᴀʀᴀʟʟᴇʟᴇᴅ ᴋɪɴᴅɴᴇꜱꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴇʟꜰʟᴇꜱꜱɴᴇꜱꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e55e11db-e45f-4f5b-bab2-184b9f0f84ef_character-cathleen-bate-nsfw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/g83hBda.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/UN3Yhl6LzaU?si=ucPAnze8DPx7O34l\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5mR1f3V.png\"></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FLSaw12.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JcTsV3x.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lwetkzC.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/horikoshiko\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ᴋᴏʜᴇɪ ʜᴏʀɪᴋᴏꜱʜɪ</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_8ce290e6-8dc1-4264-9a56-96487f91cfa9.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1842,"messages":23301,"created_at":"2024-06-30T21:57:34.554502+00:00"}